creator: Vamoos Ltd
descriptionHtml:
The SmoothRed Travel app lets you access your trip documentation and destination information while you’re away, in one place. Here is what you will find:
• Your personalised travel itinerary including flight details
• Day-by-day trip summary
• Live flight updates
• Trip countdown
• Weather forecast
• Essential travel documents, including our recommended destination restaurant list
• Local maps
• Add notes on your photographs and share with your friends and family on social media channels

All these features once downloaded are available offline.

Have a great trip!
